If the `ai-skills/` directory is empty or missing, initialize the submodule first: `git submodule update --init ai-skills`

When adding or modifying Kinetic Platform skills, make changes inside `ai-skills/` and submit a pull request to the `kineticdata/kinetic-platform-ai-skills` repository so all projects benefit from the update.

